            <description><![CDATA[官骑好价返场，住宿的宝也能实现酸奶自由 <br> <br>纯甄 原味风味酸奶200g*共32盒【拍2件】￥89.9 <br> <br>折才2.8/盒❗线下一箱10盒的竟然要78大洋<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[允悲]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_yunbei-a14a649db8.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>也太坑了吧！纯甄是纯正生牛乳发酵的，每包含有180mg钙和5.6g蛋白质，浓稠顺滑，酸酸甜甜的营养又好嚯 <br> <br>常温储存180天，日常拿来拌麦片坚果当早餐、拌水果沙拉，天气热了还可以扔进冰箱冻成雪糕<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[馋嘴]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_chanzui-fc1acc341b.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><img style="" src="https://wx3.sinaimg.cn/large/623e5fccgy1h13vyjpd4gj20j60j60u6.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx1.sinaimg.cn/large/623e5fccgy1h13vyk9pohj20gt0mk40h.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx2.sinaimg.cn/large/623e5fccgy1h13vyks4onj20f00i9wfr.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx2.sinaimg.cn/large/623e5fccgy1h13vyl7y7dj20j60j6myu.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx3.sinaimg.cn/large/623e5fccgy1h13vylohukj20gm0kd750.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx1.sinaimg.cn/large/623e5fccgy1h13vym5n2jj20j60j6mz9.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx1.sinaimg.cn/large/623e5fccgy1h13vymprysj2010010jr5.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://wx4.sinaimg.cn/large/623e5fccgy1h13vyn6t3oj2010010jr5.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
